  "response": "Here are some useful Android tips and tricks:\n\n1. Battery and Performance\n- Use battery saver mode\n- Optimize background apps\n- Enable dark mode to save battery\n- Clear app cache regularly\n- Disable unnecessary animations\n\n2. Security\n- Use Google Play Protect\n- Enable two-factor authentication\n- Lock apps with secure folder\n- Use a VPN for privacy\n- Install apps only from official store\n\n3. Customization\n- Use Nova Launcher for advanced customization\n- Create custom quick settings\n- Use adaptive icons\n- Change default apps\n- Customize navigation buttons\n\n4. Productivity\n- Use Google Assistant shortcuts\n- Enable digital wellbeing features\n- Use split-screen mode\n- Utilize Google Lens\n- Set up quick replies\n\n5. Hidden Features\n- Enable developer options\n- Use screen recording\n- Cast screen to other devices\n- Use Google Translate offline\n- Take scrolling screenshots\n\n6. Storage Management\n- Use Google Files app\n- Backup photos to cloud\n- Move apps to SD card\n- Use Files Go for cleanup\n- Uninstall unused apps\n\n7. Connectivity\n- Quick Wi-Fi sharing\n- Use nearby sharing\n- Connect Bluetooth devices easily\n- Use mobile hotspot efficiently\n\nThese tips can help improve your Android experience and device performance.",
